cs.MM, cs.NI, cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.SY 

The paper deals with the transmission of multi-view videos over wireless networks, which involves multimedia (cs.MM) and networking (cs.NI) aspects. The use of view synthesis for multicast opportunities involves computer vision (cs.CV) and information theory (cs.IT) concepts. The optimization problem formulation and solution involve control systems (cs.SY) techniques.
